Package: IrregLong
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of longitudinal data with irregular observation times
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2015-07-23
Author: Eleanor Pullenayegum
Maintainer: Eleanor Pullenayegum <eleanor.pullenayegum@sickkids.ca>
Description: This package contains functions to analyse longitudinal data
    for which the times of observation are random variables that are potentially
    associated with the outcome process. The package includes inverse-intensity
    weighting and multiple outputation methods.
Depends:
    survival, geepack, frailtypack, R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
